    "body": "I think that Dapps can call \"balanceOf\" without gas to get the balance of the sender before \"transfer\".\r\nIf the user is intentionally paying more than his own amount, why we should save the gas for him?\r\nAnd one more line code cause everyone need pay more gas, Is it fair？",
